strings.Value: "Last time I got beat up this bad was when I disagreed with chief shatshank. Bones sticking through skin, just like now!"
"Ow, almost got an eye out. Is it pricey to get a new one? Nah, don't need it, eyeless Hero is better than intact Hero!"
"You worry me when you talk like that. Let me tend to your wounds."
"Too much hassle for the one who is so close to his end."
"Scars are valuable trophies! You should be proud when you get new ones from a great fight!"
"Stop showing me every last of your bruises! I will be seeing nightmares after these demonstrations!"
